docs/outreach/LETTERS-BR-*.md
docs/outreach/EMAIL-TEMPLATES.md
docs/outreach/DEMO-FLOW.md
docs/outreach/TRACKER.md

# Internal strategy / planning specs — not for external readers.
docs/superpowers/

